data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS.Welcome to your dream home in Willow Creek Plantation! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a true gem with numerous upgrades.Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the elegance of hardwood floors and crown molding throughout the newly painted living area. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring newer Frigidaire Gallery appliances, granite countertops, custom Wellington cabinets, and a charming coffee nook.The outdoor space is equally impressive with a screened-in porch, a treehouse, and a shed. The 8-foot privacy fence ensures your peace and tranquility. The extended driveway provides ample parking, including space for an RV, and the large 2-car garage offers plenty of storage.This home is not just a beauty but also a practical choice with a new AC in 2023, a 2020 air handler, and a newer water heater. Plus, the community offers a pool for you to enjoy.Don't miss the opportunity to make this incredible Willow Creek Plantation home yours!
